  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1293815">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1293815/" class="title-link">换一个角度思考中国的文明起源、民族关系和历史发展</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1293815"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/abing/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1404017-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/abing/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">abing</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-01-30"
      class="main-meta">2008-01-30 22:28:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1293815_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      和国内外许多关于游牧民族和文明起源的论著不同，拉铁摩尔在这本书里超越了传统“游牧民族”和“定居农民”的二分观念，站在一个更高的层面上论述了有关中国文明起源、民族演变和历史发展等等关键性问题。或许作者所持观点显得有些折衷，还有待商榷，但却契合协同学等系统...

